REF Securities & Co. Key Developments

REF Securities To Discuss Strategic Alternatives
Nov 2 15
REF Securities & Co. has engaged in discussions with management, the Board, and other shareholders regarding ways to maximize shareholder value. REF Securities & Co. intends to engage more substantively with management, the Board and other relevant parties on matters concerning the business, assets, capitalization, financial condition, operations, management, strategy and future plans of the company. REF Securities & Co. may also discuss strategic alternatives with interested parties to propose or consider extraordinary transactions including, without limitation, a merger, divesting certain assets, effectuating and participating in a "going private" transaction, or exploring the sale of the company.


