Lexis Securities Mosaic Tutorial: SEC Comment Letters
This is a tutorial video highlighting how to use the comment letters searching feature to locate and access correspondence threads and comment letters.





Lexis Securities Mosaic Tutorial: Lexis Securities Mosaic for M&A
This is a tutorial video demonstrating how you can use Lexis Securities Mosaic to stay up to date on current mergers & acquisitions information.





Lexis Securities Mosaic Tutorial: Dodd-Frank Tracker
This tutorial video shows how Lexis Securities Mosaic can help you keep up with the torrent of rulemaking generated by the Dodd-Frank Act with our exclusive rulemaking tracker.





Lexis Securities Mosaic Tutorial: Law Firm Relationships
This is a tutorial video highlighting how to use the Law Firm Relationships search page to discover who is working for whom in the legal industry, and learn more about these relationships as you pinpoint relevant filings disclosed by the SEC.





Lexis Securities Mosaic Tutorial: SEC Filings
This is a tutorial video highlighting on how to use the SEC filings search feature to locate specific company filings submitted to the Securities and Exchange Commission going back to 1994 with pre-EDGAR paper filings archived from 1960 to 1993.





Lexis Securities Mosaic Tutorial: Agreements & Exhibits Searching
This is a tutorial video highlighting how to use the agreements & exhibiting searching feature to locate documents including stock purchase agreements, credit agreements, indenture, company bylaws and press releases.





Lexis Securities Mosaic Tutorial: Laws, Rules & Agency Materials
This is a tutorial video highlighting how to use the Laws, Rules & Agency Materials page to stay on top of federal laws and administrative rules, the federal register, congressional legislation and federal agencies and oversight bodies.





Lexis Securities Mosaic Tutorial: Risk Factors
This is a tutorial video highlighting how to use Lexis Securities Mosaic to identify targeted disclosures of risk and find model precedent language among more than 450,000 risk factors disclosed in SEC filings.
















